OL,3,CNo more 'saying no to Wales', says
OL,4,CPlaid Cymru leader at manifesto launch
OL,6,FThe party is promising universal
OL,7,Fchildcare from 9 months and new
OL,8,Fsurgical hubs to cut waiting times,
OL,9,FITV News' Wales Reporter Rhys Williams
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FLaunching their manifesto in a city
OL,13,Ffamous for its football team's
OL,14,Fspectacular climb up the league
OL,15,Fpyramid, Plaid Cymru thinks now is the
OL,16,Ftime for its own rise to power.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
