PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775782987
OL,3,CNo more 'saying no to Wales', says
OL,4,CPlaid Cymru leader at manifesto launch
OL,6,FThe First Minister, Eluned Morgan's
OL,7,Fpitch is that Wales needs stability
OL,8,Fand to focus on the cost of living.
OL,9,FThe party is also promising to spend
OL,10,F#4bn on new hospitals in Cardiff,
OL,11,FWrexham and west Wales.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Conservatives are
OL,14,Fcampaigning on a 1p cut in income tax,
OL,15,Fan M4 relief road near Newport and a
OL,16,Fpledge to reverse the expansion of the
OL,17,FSenedd, while the Liberal Democrats
OL,18,Falso hope a more proportional system
OL,19,Fwill help it to convert votes into
OL,20,Fseats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
